{"tid":2301388,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天主教正義和平委員會批評政府警隊專欄文章 遭《公教報》粗暴刪去","createTime":"2020-11-26T09:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T10:22:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2e33b0bd4451f47165a7a6632d2ea1336159e1","tid":2301388,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"一向積極在社會議題發聲的天主教正義和平委員會，遭教區刊物《公教報》粗暴刪去專欄內容。正委會今午在社交平台Facebook發文，指《公教報》在未得該會同意下，擅自刪除部份內容並強行出版。當中3段涉及批評政府和警隊的部份被刪去，包括港府在反修例運動裏，「作出令社會擔心出現人道危機的決定」、港府漠視人性尊嚴，及警察輕視人命價值等字句。該報總編輯回應時表示作出改動前已知會該會，又否認收高層指示要河蟹正委。<br />\n<br />\n《公教報》每期刊登由正委會供稿的義筆容辭專欄，正委會今午在社交平台Facebook發文，指《公教報》在未得該會同意下，擅自刪除部份內容並強行出版，「本會茲嚴正申明該修訂後的文章與本會無關，特此澄清，以正視聽。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/AORFE2MKE5FFRMVAMFDQNMUMR4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2FAORFE2MKE5FFRMVAMFDQNMUMR4%2F&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjDsAEF7kNGMxk903cO3jeS8%3D&h=0f1c2a41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201126%2FAORFE2MKE5FFRMVAMFDQNMUMR4%2F&h=2bd3eb5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201126/AORFE2MKE5FFRMVAMFDQNMUMR4/</a>"},{"pid":"3bcbc6e5878fb828e5276565ec5c2468388c68b0","tid":2301388,"uid":44209,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9r8gus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9r8gus.jpg&h=9d21558a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80237566e358c43595379171656f262ab56a5fd7","tid":2301388,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b351d22a2fd92f04a18edbdb0fe836919a5910db","tid":2301388,"uid":143230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"狗：獎勵既男幼幼已經送到你張床"},{"pid":"9fe12a149681b06bb4a